# Hero images directory
# Place your optimized hero images here

## Recommended image sizes:
- hero-mobile.jpg (640x960px, ~50-80KB)
- hero-tablet.jpg (1024x768px, ~100-150KB)
- hero-desktop.jpg (1920x1080px, ~200-300KB)
- hero-desktop-large.jpg (2560x1440px, ~300-400KB)

## Optimization tips:
1. Use JPEG for photographs (quality: 75-85%)
2. Use WebP for better compression (save both formats)
3. Use online tools:
   - TinyPNG.com
   - Squoosh.app
   - ImageOptim (Mac)
   - GIMP/Photoshop export for web

